              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">箓灵</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/0af9611ff900342f560004bd85d6e766_8563901926153231655.png",
                "id": "talent60286",
                "key": "神女遣灵真诀",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神女遣灵真诀"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此召唤物在场时：</span>敌方角色受到的<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素伤害</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2882505687012034338.png",
                "id": "talent41870",
                "key": "箓灵",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/0729bd2530214665f6a30676963e3d6f_319507714412692396.png",
                "title": "箓灵"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_4508319043262604037.png",
                "id": "talent47573",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">冰翎</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>我方角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>+1。（包括角色引发的<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>扩散伤害）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3009804904793570347.png",
